<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Link Generator</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/styleUsers.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="text-center user-modal m-auto">
      <h3 class="">Get Your Achievement Role on Discord</h3>
      <form
        action="/users/invite/<%= invite_id%>/<%= created_for%>"
        method="post"
      >
        <input
          name="discord_id"
          type="text"
          placeholder="Discord ID"
          class="mb-2 m-auto mt-3 form-control"
        />
        <input
          name="discord_username"
          type="text"
          placeholder="Discord Username"
          class="m-auto form-control"
        />
        <button type="submit" class="btn mb-3 btn-orange w-100 mt-3">
          Get Your Discord Role Link
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="instructions text-center mt-5">
      <h1>Instructions</h1>
      <div class="w-50 m-auto"
        >Congratulations on your Achievement in Crypto Legions! You can now
        obtain your special role in our Discord server, proving your amazing
        achievement. Â  Here are the instructions how to find your Discord ID and
        Discord Username to copy in the fields above, and how to get verified on
        Discord to obtain your Achievement role.</div
      >
      <h2 class="mt-4">STEP 1: COPY DISCORD ID</h2>
      <h2 class="mt-4">STEP 2: COPY DISCORD NAME</h2>
      <h2 class="mt-4">STEP 3: VERIFY INSIDE DISCORD</h2>
      <h2 class="mt-4">STEP 4: ACCESS EXCLUSIVE CHAT</h2>
      <div class="text-center m-auto w-50">
        Now you have access to an exclusive chat channel only for players who
        got a similar Achievement as you. Congratulations! Happy hunting on
        planet Nicah!</div
      >
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
